{"title":"森林在呼啸","authors":["顾工"],"dates":[{"year":1965,"month":10,"day":21}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"森林在呼啸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顾工"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"森林、森林，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无边无际的森林，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无头无尽的森林，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们穿越过"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一株株巨大的树，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"行进，行进……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抬头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"望不见星，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"密密的枝杈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浓浓的树叶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遮没了穹顶；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"低头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看不到地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蓬蓬的刺丛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"繁生的草菌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"盖没了路径。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每跨一步，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都要用钢枪拨草；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每进一尺，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都要用刺刀斩荆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"森林，森林，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无边无际的森林，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无头无尽的森林……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在赤道线上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也有这样的森林，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那里的革命弟兄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也在行进、行进……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"棕榈丛中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闪出磨亮的长矛；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"椰子树下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"露出火焰般的红缨！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黑色的皮肤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"溶进黑色的夜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正在杀出一个"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红光满天的黎明！……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在越南南方，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也有这样的森林，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那里的战斗英雄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也在行进、行进……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"芭蕉丛中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有美国飞机的残骸；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"芒果树下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有横倒的美国士兵。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"缴侵略者的枪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要侵略者的命，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命的凯歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在飘荡，在飞腾！……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世界上不知有多少森林，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每座浩瀚的森林，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都在呼唤着："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命呵，革命！……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"森林呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是人民的屏风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是战士的掩体。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"森林呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你嗅到野兽的血腥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你看到豺狼的脚印，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你也怒发冲冠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你也挺身而立，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你也在和我们的队伍，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一起行进，行进……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"森林呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"游击战士在行进，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战斗英雄在行进，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"越来越壮大的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命队伍在行进……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"森林呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在你的深处，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在你的篝火旁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在你的营地上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有支同样的进行曲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有支同样的国际歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在飘荡，在飞腾！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}